<table  border=0 cellpadding=2 cellspacing=0 awidth=100%><a name=10025645544709></a><form action=http://eqdb.allakhazam.com/strategy/mrate.pl name=f10025645544709><tr><td id=headerrow><a id=sj href=classes.html?class=3&mid=10025645544709>RE: What do i need</a> <a id=fs8 href=classes.html?class=3&mid=10025645544709#post><img src=http://everquest.allakhazam.com/static/reply.gif border=0 alt="Reply..." height=16 width=16></a></td><td align=right id=headerrow valign=bottom><span id=notbold>By:</span> <a href=poster.html?user=35651><span id=Guru>Keyeluke</span></a>, <span id=Guru>Guru</span><br><span id=notbold>498 posts</td></tr>
	   <tr><td colspan=1 id=headerrow>Posted @ Mon, Oct 8th 2:09 PM 2001</td>
	   <td id=headerrow align=right><span id=notbold>Score</span>: Excellent<span id=notbold>[5.00]</span></td></tr>
	   <tr><td colspan=2>Monks have only 3 melee skills - Hand-to-Hand, One Hand Blunt, and Two Hand Blunt.&nbsp;&nbsp;You won't need to chase these religiously till you get to your low teens, but as soon as you see whichever you use mostly max out, that's a sign that it's time to practice the others up each level.  Keep all 3 maxed or within 10 points of maxed each level, and you'll be VERY happy later on.<br><br>Sneak, Safe Fall, Feign Death, Instill Doubt, Sense Heading, and Bind Wound all are core Monk skills, and you should take time to work on them as you level up.  Swimming can be trained to useful levels in a day - just find a nice peaceful pool of water (the Freeport canal outside the Monk guild is my favorite), swim at a wall, adjust your heading till you're not drifting, hit auto run, and walk away from your computer for a few hours.<br><br>Make sure you put a point into every new skill you get as you level up, and always use your newest special attack.  Save skill points for Feign Death and Instill Doubt.  Plan to burn 23 skill points on Instill Doubt, a bunch on Feign Death before it, then save points after that to train up Flying Kick at level 30.<br>&nbsp;<br>Keyeluke<br>Strange Brew - Druzzil Ro<br><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=27415" target=_new>http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=27415</a></td></tr>
